data.title: Rock Band Tier List

data.description: This is my Rock Band tier list!

tierdata.name: Foo Fighters - Learn to Fly
tierdata.desc: It's just such an amazing song and it's incredibly fun to play!

tierdata.name: SoundGarden - Black Hole Sun
tierdata.desc: Has the power to put anyone into a chance with its wicked guitar and heavenly singing

tierdata.name: Faith No More - Epic
tierdata.desc: An incredibly fun song with an absolutely beautiful ending

tierdata.name: Coheed and Cambria - Welcome Home
tierdata.desc: You can just FEEL the emotion penetrating your earholes.
